text: Romeu Pellicciari, also known as Romeu (born in Jundiai, March 26, 1911 - died in São Paulo, July 15, 1971)CBF profile was an association footballer. He played as a striker. == References == Category:1911 births Category:1971 deaths Category:Footballers from São Paulo (state)
